\s0 \qj\snext0\f1\fs24\b0\i0\fi567\li0\ri0 "About the same as my daughter-my daughter was a junior when the girl was killed, so, sixteen, seventeen."\par
\s0 \qj\snext0\f1\fs24\b0\i0\fi567\li0\ri0 Virgil said, "Huh. Another mystery. I wonder if I could clear it all out, with another order of home fries?"\par
\s0 \qj\snext0\f1\fs24\b0\i0\fi567\li0\ri0 "You'd clear something out, but I don't think it'd be the murder case," the man in the booth said.\par
\s0 \qj\snext0\f1\fs24\b0\i0\fi567\li0\ri0 A waitress said, "Hey. No pie for you, Earl."\par
