\s0 \qj\snext0\f1\fs24\b0\i0\fi567\li0\ri0 "The point is, you don't have to buy her story. You've got a perfectly good and legitimate reason to tear her house apart-her own testimony that she was there, at what you suspect might have been a murder. Go look at every piece of paper and letter and e-mail and picture she's got in her house. Go do it. Maybe you can find something that'll unravel the whole thing for you."\par
