\s0 \qj\snext0\f1\fs24\b0\i0\fi567\li0\ri0 "Walk careful," Virgil said, and the two of them tiptoed away.\par
\s0 \qj\snext0\f1\fs24\b0\i0\fi567\li0\ri0 Outside again, Schickel called for a fire truck, and Virgil got the other cars backed away from the house. Then they sat and watched, one minute, three minutes, and Virgil said, "Maybe we could have gotten him out."\par
