\s0 \qj\snext0\f1\fs24\b0\i0\fi567\li0\ri0 As with the Einstadt house, there were lights: they drove up the driveway and found a pickup sitting next to the side door. They stopped, and Virgil said, "Run it," and Jenkins got out of his truck and pointed his M16 at the house.\par
