\s0 \qj\snext0\f1\fs24\b0\i0\fi567\li0\ri0 Helen said to Virgil, "He took me upstairs and he was so ready, he was like a bull; he pulled all my clothes off and he ripped my blouse, not on the seam, but right across the fabric so I can't fix it, and it'll always have a rip in it."\par
