\s0 \qj\snext0\f1\fs24\b0\i0\fi567\li0\ri0 The muzzle of the gun never moved, but Alma said to her father, "What do you have to say for him?"\par
\s0 \qj\snext0\f1\fs24\b0\i0\fi567\li0\ri0 Emmett Einstadt said, "Women are supposed to serve men. That's why God put them on earth. Rooney might not be the best we got, but he tries hard enough. You'da got used to him if you'd gave him some time."\par
\s0 \qj\snext0\f1\fs24\b0\i0\fi567\li0\ri0 She shook her head and said, "I don't believe I would have. I started out liking Jake, and ended up hating him; I started out hating Rooney. How you could ever give us to him, I'll never understand. How many times did we say no?"\par
