\s0 \qj\snext0\f1\fs24\b0\i0\fi567\li0\ri0 Virgil's cell phone rang. They all jumped, and a smile might have flickered over Alma Flood's face. She said, "Well, answer it. Or the ringing will drive us crazy."\par
